query: SELECT r.id, r.room_id, DATE(r.reservation_date) as date, r.start_time, r.end_time, s1.name as student1_name, s1.class_number as student1_class, s2.name as student2_name, s2.class_number as student2_class FROM reservations r LEFT JOIN students s1 ON r.student1_id = s1.id LEFT JOIN students s2 ON r.student2_id = s2.id WHERE DATE(r.reservation_date) = '2026-02-21';
